snippet.title: 13 Sentinels: Aegis Rim - 13 Stories Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: 13: Sentinels: Aegis Rim is coming to the PlayStation 4 on September 8! The 13 Stories Trailer introduces the protagonists of the intertwining stories.
